item.title: Runescape hacks, for real?
item.dc:creator: @Mopman Mopman
item.description:
@Mopman wrote:

[quote=“Eh Pretty Easy, post:7, topic:131636”][quote author=sidishere link=topic=182418.msg1662350#msg1662350 date=1186659149]
you can…pm admin
[/quote]Ummm, no he can’t. Admins won’t do any name changes anymore unless you have a very good reason for it, which he doesn’t.

[quote author=tryed to hack it link=topic=182418.msg1662158#msg1662158 date=1186650373]
lol, thats not really spam, i was asking if the hacks for runescape (not like item spawners) but, idk to learn like… u know the party hat thing that happend? were u could use died silk and a knife to make a party hat?

i wanna see if i could hack in there to learn that sfuf
[/quote]Seems like you’ve spent your life googling for runescape cheats and found that shit from there? THAT’S NOT TRUE, when RS2 came out the items that people had on their accounts were transferred to rs2. People started abusing it by making a new account and going into rsc and giving the rares to the account and logging into rs2 so that 2 accounts had the rares. They kept doing it on and on and then Jagex had a huge mass ban, happy now?[/quote]

That’s not 100% true. This dupe did happen, but only in the beta - no items made it into “real” RS2, nobody was mass-banned, the beta was wiped when the real game launched and the duped items went with it.
